title: 820-01700 no boot
message:
Do you get all AWAKE and SLPS2R voltages?
If yes, try DFU revive.
If no important data to save, go directly for DFU restore.

Also check if G3S and SSD voltages come on.

title: 820-01700 no boot

title: 820-01700 no boot
message:
Try with the board alone on the desk; nothing connected.
It should appear on DFU even without charger.

SWK003 should be closed when charger is connected.
Need to open it after few seconds...

title: 820-01700 no boot
message:
I tried with board alone on desk first, then in chassi after i saw the note about touchbar sometimes needing to be connected.

SWK003 was closed when i connected DFU and charger cable, never popped up in AC2 so i never opened it, do i need to open regardless of it showing in AC2?
